==English==

===Noun===
'''sterilize'''

# To deprive a male or female the ability to procreate.
# To make unable to produce. To make unprofitable.
# ''(Biology):'' To destroy all spores or germs in (an organic fluid or mixture), as by heat, so as to prevent the development of bacterial or other organisms.

